title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Nov 30 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Nov 30 2021
description:
Former Speaker of the House, Newt Gingrich, makes a surprise phone call to join C&B to discuss the media covering up the Waukesha Christmas parade attack. Is the country waking up to the fact that Big Government socialism doesn't work? Will Biden repeat the Clinton strategy of 1996? Jussie Smollett may go to jail for fake MAGA hate crime. Buck: Should Smollett get three years in prison? Hell, yeah, he should. Absolutely. Why hasn't Biden visited the victims of the Waukesha Christmas parade attack? Psaki: A visit requires too many assets. No one is allowed to talk about the motive of Darrell Brooks Jr.
